text: Wajdi Kechrida (born 5 November 1995) is a Tunisian professional footballer who plays as a right back for Étoile Sportive du Sahel and the Tunisia. ==Club career== Kechrida made his professional debut for Étoile Sportive du Sahel in a 3–0 Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1 win over ES Zarzis on 10 September 2016. ==International career== Kechrida made his debut for the Tunisia national team in a 2019 Africa Cup of Nations qualification 4–0 win over Eswatini on 22 March 2019. ==Career statistics== ===International=== {| class="wikitable" style="text-align:center" |- |colspan="3"|Tunisia national team |- !Year!!Apps!!Goals |- |2019||8||0 |- !Total||8||0 |} ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Nice Category:Tunisian footballers Category:Tunisia international footballers Category:Tunisia under-23 international footballers Category:French footballers Category:French people of Tunisian descent Category:Étoile Sportive du Sahel players Category:Tunisian Ligue Professionnelle 1 players Category:Association football midfielders Category:2019 Africa Cup of Nations players
